                          "content":  "\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e/....\u003cbr\u003eCharly Rhoades writes:\u003cbr\u003e\u003eAlso, why the labelling of _Pure,_Impure_ as an EP?\u003cbr\u003e\u003eBecause it only has 6 songs?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eIt\u0027s actually a compilation of the \u0026#34;Plainsong\u0026#34; single (the first 3 songs)with the three remixes, which I don\u0027t believe were released separately. Sosince it\u0027s more of a \u0026#34;single with bonus remix tracks\u0026#34; I guess they didn\u0027tfeel like calling it an LP.\u003cbr\u003e..../\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThe mixes were available seperately domestically (UK). In some shops theCD was priced at single price L4.50, and at some places at mini-album priceL8ish. To me \u0026#34;EP\u0026#34; just means a 12\u0026#34; or a CD single (more like a CD single).I prefer to clasify things is single, mini album, and lp.\u003cbr\u003e   __         __     __         __    \u003cbr\u003e  /\\ \\       /\\_\\   /\\ \\       /\\ \\      \u0027I may have signed away my life  /  \\ \\     / / /  /  \\ \\     /  \\ \\     but my opinions are still my own\u0027/ /\\ \\ \\   / / /  / /\\ \\ \\   / /\\ \\_\\ \u003cbr\u003e\\ \\/  \\_\\ / /_/   \\ \\/  \\_\\ / / / / /       alan.scully@london.sbi.com\u003cbr\u003e \\  /\\/_/ \\ \\ \\    \\  /\\/_/ \\/_/ / /       Technical Services Group BTO\u003cbr\u003e  \\ \\_\\    \\ \\_\\    \\ \\_\\     / / /   Salomon Brothers International Limited   \\/_/     \\/_/     \\/_/     \\/_/   work 0171 721 3515 -- home 0181 672 9319\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e \u003cbr\u003e"
