                         "from":  "Billy Cordray \u003cultra@crl.com\u003e",
                         "dateString":  "Mon, 10 Oct 1994 13:21:17 -0700 (PDT)",
                         "content":  "\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\tCould somebody give me info T:me records?  Like an address, phone \u003cbr\u003e#, discography, etc...  Peace...\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e"
