                          "content":  "\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eorginal:\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003e Herb dried to puurfection \u003cbr\u003e\u003e herb placed in golden globe flame\u003cbr\u003e\u003e flickers ingnites said leafy leaf\u003cbr\u003e\u003e                                  puffy puff of herb - AHhh\u003cbr\u003e\u003e                                  bean bag chair soooooo\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eremix:\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003egolden lobes licked nearflames purrs\u003cbr\u003eleaves mounds of bean bags ignited in the night\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003e                              a horrendous joy\u003cbr\u003e\u003e    the inspired moon has mangled\u003cbr\u003e\u003e    and to steal\u003cbr\u003e\u003e     a jumping infant\u003cbr\u003e\u003e       a jumping infant, a bicycle\u003cbr\u003e\u003e       by the inner-city dumptruck\u003cbr\u003e\u003e       and has created\u003cbr\u003e\u003e       to grasp\u003cbr\u003e\u003e         only\u003cbr\u003e\u003e         to freeze\u003cbr\u003e\u003e         a bicycle has lost\u003cbr\u003e\u003e         sometimes has plumbed\u003cbr\u003e\u003e         and rapidly passing\u003cbr\u003e\u003e         a jumping infant has hung. \u003cbr\u003e\u003e                                                  - nigel migraine\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eremix:\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003ethe infant tears the uninspired moon to\u003cbr\u003eshreds, its joy a horror\u003cbr\u003ein our eyes\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e~*-,._.,-*~\u0027`^`\u0027~*-,._.,-*~\u0027`^`\u0027~*-,._.,-*~\u0027`^`\u0027~*-,._.,-*~\u0027`^`\u0027~*-,._.,-*~    Justin McHale                                    jmchale@gmu.edu     ~*-,._.,-*~\u0027`^`\u0027~*-,._.,-*~\u0027`^`\u0027~*-,._.,-*~\u0027`^`\u0027~*-,._.,-*~\u0027`^`\u0027~*-,._.,-*~                                           (c) Copyright 1994 Justin McHale\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e"
