  "amb_1994_08_7":  {
                        "subject":  "UPDATE! net-musician compilation...",
                        "from":  "interlab@Mtech.csd.uwm.edu (InterLAB rekkids)",
                        "dateString":  "Tue, 16 Aug 1994 20:56:47 -0500 (CDT)",
                        "content":  "\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eUPDATE! on InterLAB rave/techno net-musician compilation\u003cbr\u003e----------------------------------------------------------------------\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e  so far we\u0027ve received more than a dozen submissions and we are\u003cbr\u003e  getting tons of support from already established musicians,\u003cbr\u003e  labels and distributors! the general response to the idea has\u003cbr\u003e  been nothing but positive and so we are very excited to get this\u003cbr\u003e  project underway. to follow are some important notes that should\u003cbr\u003e  answer some of the questions people have been asking about us...\u003cbr\u003e  if you have ANY other questions, please e-mail us (please note\u003cbr\u003e  our new address below)...\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e  \t\t\t\t\tacidophile \u0026 modE\u003cbr\u003e\t\t\t\t\t InterLAB rekkids\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e  SUBMISSION INFO\u003cbr\u003e  ---------------------------------------------------------------\u003cbr\u003e  we expect to release the compilation in late september, so get\u003cbr\u003e  your submissions to us soon. send them to:\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\t\t\t\tInterLAB rekkids\u003cbr\u003e\t\t\t\t2582 stowell unit S\u003cbr\u003e\t\t\t\tmilwaukee WI 53211\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e  all formats acceptable (cassette, DAT, vinyl, or even VHS).\u003cbr\u003e  please include all vitals including booking info if any. of\u003cbr\u003e  course you must include an e-mail address...\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e  MORE INFO ON RELEASE\u003cbr\u003e  ---------------------------------------------------------------\u003cbr\u003e  the compilation will contain approx. 90 minutes of original\u003cbr\u003e  material by net-musicians ONLY. (our label will always be for\u003cbr\u003e  net-musicians ONLY). the tape will be DIGITALLY MASTERED and\u003cbr\u003e  will be available for $5 including postage. the tape will be\u003cbr\u003e  distributed over the net as well as at events/parties and any\u003cbr\u003e  interested retail outlets. but it will never cost more than\u003cbr\u003e  $5. the object here is not to make money, but to get the power\u003cbr\u003e  of the net surging through as many of us as possible and to\u003cbr\u003e  work with musicians on upcoming InterLAB releases on vinyl.\u003cbr\u003e  initially 500 copies will be made available and then copies\u003cbr\u003e  will be made on a per order basis. extra copies will also be\u003cbr\u003e  made for promotional purposes. let us know if you need more\u003cbr\u003e  release details. in late september we will post track listings\u003cbr\u003e  along with ordering details. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\t\tWE ARE STILL ACCEPTING SUBMISSIONS!!!  \u003cbr\u003e  \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e  ADDRESS CHANGE\u003cbr\u003e  ---------------------------------------------------------------\u003cbr\u003e  we now have a seperate address for InterLAB, so please take\u003cbr\u003e  note of our new address:\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e                        InterLAB@Mtech.csd.uwm.edu\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e  InterLAB MAILING-LIST\u003cbr\u003e  ---------------------------------------------------------------\u003cbr\u003e  to be sure you dont miss future details about this and other\u003cbr\u003e  InterLAB releases you may want to be added to our mailing list.\u003cbr\u003e  dont worry, its not gonna stuff-up your mailbox! just e-mail\u003cbr\u003e  us if you want to subscribe...\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e  peace/respect/unity through dance...\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e  acidophile \u0026 modE                                          InterLAB rekkids-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\t\t\t\t\t\t   InterLAB@Mtech.csd.uwm.edu\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t  2582 stowell unit S\u003cbr\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t  milwwaukee wi 53211\u003cbr\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t 414.964.7590\u003cbr\u003e"
                    },
