                          "dateString":  "13 Oct 1994 19:33:54 -0400 (EDT)",
                          "content":  "\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003erecently i applied for a dj position at my schools radio station and\u003cbr\u003egot a show.   Ambient Lounge is the title and the music that i must\u003cbr\u003eplay should, of course be in compliance with the name.  unfortunately\u003cbr\u003e(or perhaps for the best) the time slot is 1-3 in the morning and \u003cbr\u003eso i will try my best to provide the listeners with most interesting\u003cbr\u003epieces so the atmosphere of the \u0027Lounge\u0027 will not be sleepish.\u003cbr\u003eif anyone has any suggestions as to which music will be appropriate,\u003cbr\u003edo send the name of the pieces and the artist\u0027s name to my personal\u003cbr\u003eaddress.      many thanks.\u003cbr\u003evictoria\u003cbr\u003e"
