  "amb_1994_10_10":  {
                         "subject":  "New Records",
                         "from":  "gamshad@tcs.com (Mohsen Gamshad)",
                         "dateString":  "Mon, 10 Oct 94 09:50:41 PDT",
                         "content":  "\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eAnd now for some new music.  Just got the second volume of Feed Your Headand man it\u0027s great, there isn\u0027t a single track that doesn\u0027t deserve\u003cbr\u003espace here; probably the best ambient comp of the year so far (on\u003cbr\u003ePlanet Dog).  Next record is by UVX: Double Helix, very nice ambient withsome beats bordering trance at parts, more up-beat than chill-out, but\u003cbr\u003eworth a definite listen.  Lastly, got the new Rising High ambient offering,Neturon 900, and it is really good.  Two tracks have beats and could\u003cbr\u003eresemble the stuff on Electronic Dub (from Rising High), but the rest\u003cbr\u003eof the music is a sound track for some space film, very nice.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eCheers,\u003cbr\u003eMohsen\u003cbr\u003e"
                     },
