  "amb_1994_09_146":  {
                          "subject":  "AMBIENT IS DEAD",
                          "from":  "DOG \u003cdog@neoneo.demon.co.uk\u003e",
                          "dateString":  "Wed, 28 Sep 1994 21:47:48 +0000",
                          "content":  "\u003cbr\u003e   AMBIENT IS  OVER\u003cbr\u003e   ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eMIX MASTER MORRIS or (BITCH MASTER MOROSE) as he is known is probably theexact reason why the so called ambient scene is dying, actually include\u003cbr\u003epeople like PETER NAMLOC,RISING HIGH,APHEX TWIN and all the other dirge\u003cbr\u003ethat trundles out week after week.\u003cbr\u003eThe problem for me is that the scene is not moving forward,well actually itis but its taking on a new shape and its not ambient,MORRIS for me is\u003cbr\u003eboring ,ok he\u0027s done some good stuff ,but surely this music can go beyondheavenly chords or wishywashy strings and spacey drums.Namlocs just as bad10-15 pounds a hit and its all dull crap.Things seemed so promising in theearly days of this rebirth, electronic artists really did try and push outthe boundries ,APHEX first few release were awsome but he got suck up hisown arse along with the media and came out with something that sounded andfelt very false,he lost his naive melodies, his sound (probaly deliberate)had a very dirty underproduced feel and not in a good way.APHEX played withthe press but was\u0027nt able to create a believable world (lucid\u003cbr\u003edreaming)+(the building of his own synths) He had it all,he had the chanceof crown,but alas i fear it has gone,the same can be said for morris,blackdog,autchre,reload(global comm)just about the whole scene,they all lack theability to project themselves beyond,its like there all happy to lick eachothers arses,this compilation album that compilation album,some kind of\u003cbr\u003eelectronic insest.Within all this a few golden strands of light shine FSOLbeing probably the most noticable.There album LIFEFORMS although soundingvery obvious (birds water bubbles goats etc) has actually shown an\u003cbr\u003einteresting progression,there use of sounds and sounds within production isreally fresh.\u003cbr\u003eBut more than there music they have elevated themselves above the pack andthis is because they managed to create a beleievable world (the graphicsthe video work and the music and media reviews) they seem to live and speaka new form of communication (there use of ISDN and silicon graphics)why\u003cbr\u003ecan\u0027t other electronic artists be more dynamic.Unless more thought and\u003cbr\u003eenergy is injected into this scene it will IT WILL\u003cbr\u003eIMPLODE*********************\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e                        I NEED MORE THAN THIS\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e********************************************************************************\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e"
                      },
