                          "content":  "\u003cbr\u003eNot to bring up an old thread, BUT....\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eFor those of you who like a bit of ambient and in other moods/times like a bitof rawk (as it is so affectionately referred to on this list) check out\u003cbr\u003eWah-Wah by JAMES and ENO, a little bit of both with much brilliance. --T"
