                          "dateString":  "Fri, 14 Oct 1994 11:53:32 -0500 (CDT)",
                          "content":  "\u003cbr\u003eOn Wed, 12 Oct 1994, root wrote:\u003cbr\u003e\u003e Higher Intelligence Agency - _CoulourReform_\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eIs this different from their Colorform release?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003ecurious-\u003cbr\u003e-thad\u003cbr\u003e"
