                         "content":  "\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003e \u003e   Aaah! (1994 album-length EP)\u003cbr\u003eSide 4 is the best. :-)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e::Matthew J. Corwine                         Online Editor, XLR8R Magazine::::mcorwine@hyperreal.com                               xlr8r@hyperreal.com::::mcorwine@u.washington.edu                  Ambient Temple of Imagination::::206.328.9368                                          atoi@hyperreal.com::\u003cbr\u003e"
