                          "content":  "\u003cbr\u003eHas anyone heard the new FAX CD called \u0026#34;Reoccuring myths of\u003cbr\u003eurban...\u0026#34;?  Any comments?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eThanks,\u003cbr\u003emohsen\u003cbr\u003e"
