                          "from":  "mwinton@uclink.berkeley.edu (Michael Winton)",
                          "dateString":  "Sun, 30 Oct 1994 10:29:48 -0800",
                          "content":  "\u003cbr\u003eAt  5:13 AM 10/30/94 -0100, CHrOmE! wrote:\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003eGreetings from Amsterdam, Chrome\u003cbr\u003e\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003eOnNow: Art \u0026 Strategy (ambient miniCD by Front242)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eHow (what) is that?  I\u0027ve never heard of it... I do have the CD single ofReligion by Front 242, with a couple mixes by the Orb on it, but I haven\u0027tseen this one... \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003emike\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eOn now:  silence (true silence, not Namlook silence:)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e"
