                          "from":  "\"marti074@gold.tc.umn.edu\" \u003cmarti074@gold.tc.umn.edu\u003e",
                          "dateString":  "Sun, 30 Oct 94 22:13:06 CST",
                          "content":  "\u003cbr\u003e\u003e\u003eOther FAX CD\u0027s I\u0027m wondering about:\u003cbr\u003e\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003e Gate/Sol\u003cbr\u003e\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eHad Gate/Sol mellow guitar (Track 1 RED?) and piano (Track 2 BLUE?) with atmosphere. Disappointed - I was expecting more Namlook type sounds,\u003cbr\u003egot rid of it, now wish I had kept it as would be nice background music\u003cbr\u003eto share with friends who aren\u0027t into techno.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eND\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e"
