                          "from":  "CAI@RASCAL.MED.HARVARD.EDU",
                          "dateString":  "Mon, 31 Oct 1994 9:22:50 -0500 (EST)",
                          "content":  "\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\tI picked up FHTT ambient compilation 3 yesterday. I liked it after\u003cbr\u003ethe first listening. Nothing is particularly novel or exciting here.\u003cbr\u003eSome beats, lots of bird noise. But overall it is a solid set of\u003cbr\u003echill out music (earphone is not included :)).\u003cbr\u003e\tMy question is: who are these artists represented on the disc? I barelyrecognize anyone. are these licensed tracks from some obscure indie labels?I just wish the liner note had provide more background info about these\u003cbr\u003epeople and their other releases.\u003cbr\u003e\tI also got Trance Europe Express 3. This set is almost all IDM/trance.\u003cbr\u003eIf you still remember TEEX2, it has many nice ambient tracks. Almost no\u003cbr\u003eambient on this sequel though.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\tLin\u003cbr\u003e"
