                          "from":  "Interstellar Groovy Dave \u003ccamde933@uidaho.edu\u003e",
                          "dateString":  "Mon, 31 Oct 1994 11:52:35 -0700 (PDT)",
                          "content":  "\u003cbr\u003e\u003e Remember, when in doubt, ask Interstellar Groovy Dave!!! He knows and sees\u003cbr\u003e\u003e and be all. \u0027Nuff said! TE ; ) Yo! IGD!\u003cbr\u003e\u003e \u003cbr\u003e\tIt\u0027s the shoes...gotta be the shoes...\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\t\t\tGroovy Dave\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eambient Footwear?   Can an entire line of ambient clothing be far off?  Hmmm...perhaps Nudity is really ambient, in which case, I\u0027m ready...8-)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e-----------*------------*-----------*-----------*---------------*------------- \\ /\u003cbr\u003e 0 0    *------------* \tcamde933@uidaho.edu   Groovy Dave\u0027s House of Fish  |     |Groovy Dave!|  241 Wallace Center    KUOI 89.3 FM Moscow\u003cbr\u003e\\___/\t*------------*\tMoscow, ID 83843      Friday\u0027s 10pm -- 2am\u003cbr\u003e\t\t\t(208) 885-8171\u003cbr\u003e\t\t\t\t\t      My Nipples Explode with Delight!\u003cbr\u003eGAT d++@ -p+ c++(++++) l u++ e+/* m* s/++ n+@ h f(+) g+ w++++ t r+ y+**/--For more silliness:  http://www.uidaho.edu/~camde933\u003cbr\u003e-----------*------------*------SPAM-*-----------*---------------*-------------\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e"
