  "amb_1994_11_222":  {
                          "subject":  "Reflective",
                          "from":  "WRENCH3191@aol.com",
                          "dateString":  "Tue, 22 Nov 1994 01:51:42 -0500",
                          "content":  "\u003cbr\u003eHere is Reflective so far:\u003cbr\u003eSpace Time Continuum: Flurescence EP REF 001 (Jonah Sharp)\u003cbr\u003eSubtropic: Throb EP REF 002\u003cbr\u003eVelocette: Microcosmik EP REF 003\u003cbr\u003eVulva: Mini Vulvette EP REF 004\u003cbr\u003eSingle Cell Orchestra: Angelic Science EP REF 005\u003cbr\u003eReagenz EP REF 006 (Jonah and Deep Space Network)\u003cbr\u003eV/A:  Ambiento REF CD001 (FAX stuff)\u003cbr\u003eThere is much, much more in the works, as Jonah spent much time in Europethis Summer making connections and a lot of music. One thing on FAX that\u0027scool is a Namlook/Sharp project called Wechselspannung (loosely translated\u0026#34;Alternating Voltage\u0026#34;). People in the Bay Area should check out my show onKFJC, 89.7 FM, FR 10P-2A. Sometime before the end of the year, I\u0027ll be doinga special on Reflective, and hope to have Jonah and the whole crew up in thestudio...\u003cbr\u003e"
                      },
