                          "dateString":  "Sun, 30 Oct 1994 16:01:46 -0800 (PST)",
                          "content":  "\u003cbr\u003eOn Mon, 17 Oct 1994, Chris Howe wrote:\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003e \u003cbr\u003e\u003e Just got\u003cbr\u003e\u003e \t23 Degrees - \u0026#34;...an endless searching for substance\u0026#34;\u003cbr\u003e\u003e \t\tlast weekend.\u003cbr\u003e\u003e \u003cbr\u003e\u003e Blissed-out, ethereal electro-dub and straight up ambient...\u003cbr\u003e\u003e the best I\u0027ve heard in a long time. \u003cbr\u003e\u003e Yay Silent Records!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eI second this.  great stuff.  Stayed in the player for two weeks straight (1 of 5) and that always means I like it a great deal, as most remain in for a day or two tops.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eOnNow: I dunno, but I think it\u0027s _Ambiento_.  =B)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e"
